<!doctype html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 4rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .subtitle { color: #666; margin-top: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: #fef3c7;
      color: #92400e;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .card {
      background: #f6f8fa;
      border: 1px solid #d0d7de;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .card { background: #161b22; border-color: #30363d; }
      .subtitle { color: #999; }
    }
    dl { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 12rem 1fr; gap: 0.4rem 1rem; margin: 0; }
    dt { color: #666; }
    code { background: rgba(127,127,127,0.15); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px; }
    ul.next-steps { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    ul.next-steps li { margin: 0.3rem 0; }
    a { color: #0969da; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { a { color: #58a6ff; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1><%= appName %> <span class="badge">DEV</span></h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Express server beží. Toto je placeholder uvítacia stránka — bude nahradená v Phase 13 (homepage).</p>

  <div class="card">
    <dl>
      <dt>Prostredie</dt><dd><code><%= env %></code></dd>
      <dt>Node.js</dt><dd><code><%= nodeVersion %></code></dd>
      <dt>Server čas (UTC)</dt><dd><code><%= serverTime %></code></dd>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <h2>Ďalšie kroky</h2>
  <ul class="next-steps">
    <li><a href="/health">/health</a> — JSON status check</li>
    <li><a href="/health/db">/health/db</a> — DB ping</li>
    <li><a href="/neexistuje">/neexistuje</a> — test 404 stránky</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Stav vývoja</h2>
  <p>Aktuálne v <strong>Phase 1.3</strong> — server beží, middleware nakonfigurovaný, cron joby naplánované, štatistiky sa zapisujú do DB.</p>
  <p>Ďalej: <strong>Phase 1.4</strong> (kostra admin layoutu) a <strong>Phase 2</strong> (prihlasovanie).</p>
</body>
</html>
